{"tid":932321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國給俄羅斯兩條路：拆除核武或修改射程 若遭拒絕將退出INF《中程導彈條約》","createTime":"2018-12-07T16:00:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T04:28:51.000Z","uid":28765,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"2c69e8329c9a3e451d6b1e4edf1ca87b607770c5","tid":932321,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:00:13.000Z","msg":"俄羅總統普京（Putin）5日才表示要與美國展開軍備競賽，美國高級官員湯普森（Andrea Thompson）於7日回應，俄羅斯必須廢棄可攜帶核彈頭的9M729巡弋飛彈及發射系統，或是修改武器射程範圍，以符合冷戰時期美蘇簽訂的《中程導彈條約》(簡稱INF)，否則美國將退出該條約。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報導，美國負責軍備控制與國際安全事務的湯普森說，「不是拆除系統或發射器，不然就是別超過射程距離」。美國駐俄羅斯大使洪博培（Jon Huntsman）對此表示，美國退出條約不代表「脫離軍備管制」，而是找尋一個可靠的合作夥伴，然而俄羅斯並不是，因為它違反了INF及其他相關條約。<br />\n<br />\n參謀首長聯席會議（JCS）主席鄧福德（Joseph Dunford）7日也於《華盛頓郵報》上警告俄羅斯，如果俄羅斯繼續違反INF，可能會妨礙新的《削減戰略武器條約》（Strategic Arms Reduction Treaty, 簡稱START）的簽訂。這項條約讓美國與俄羅斯在2001年時，拆除了雙方當時存在的8成戰略核武器。<br />\n<br />\n鄧福德說，當雙方的基礎是建立在不遵守INF條約的情況下，他很難想像在擴大(新START條約)方面取得進展。報導同時也指出，除非雙方同意執行條約內的延期5年選項，否則條約將於預定2021年2月5日到期，到時候所有武器限制將全面解除。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181207/1324962.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181207%2F1324962.htm&d=UCioU7u5XOKmUJjcFOVHvsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2cecc7aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181207/1324962.htm</a>"},{"pid":"f45968cdf41df6244a1cd8e1d618000949633800","tid":932321,"uid":3646,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:07:25.000Z","msg":"America number one <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd390dc239214fb4070ce56fc1725fff9aeeeac0","tid":932321,"uid":210851,"like":22,"dislike":6,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e40ec5ed45fb2ff9acfdec1cadffa7f34473990","tid":932321,"uid":66324,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"quote":{"pid":"fd390dc239214fb4070ce56fc1725fff9aeeeac0","tid":932321,"uid":210851,"like":22,"dislike":6,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:16:34.000Z","msg":"咁任何國家都係架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76086a71a1fa78f8b178408e575d3ad0c5e9aae2","tid":932321,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:16:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"159f5240b1bc6cbc79ef43207dacbcd20d0e93ab","tid":932321,"uid":92178,"like":3,"dislike":16,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:17:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ee613c3e1194b429a2f83311f11db256eb327c10","tid":932321,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:18:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e324e668e47e1e38d70e6d0a8e70df55ceaa6104","tid":932321,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:19:36.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8237013b74b2e7cf0ef4665dad6ce509eb528674","tid":932321,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:19:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"824c2aec51a8d5b3dd8d45479b87fe37b14f6f74","tid":932321,"uid":4392,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:22:06.000Z","msg":"俄佬d 垃圾飛機片就咪撚post 出黎啦, 笑撚死人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2114d2f614ef0fac1da23b5d19ef520b82b99eef","tid":932321,"uid":83623,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"fd390dc239214fb4070ce56fc1725fff9aeeeac0","tid":932321,"uid":210851,"like":22,"dislike":6,"score":16,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:14:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-07T16:22:07.000Z","msg":"而家係叫俄羅斯拆中程彈道，指射程唔到美國但到到歐洲國家，INF 意義就係NATO 歐洲國家同俄羅斯戰略平衡，係NATO入面只係需要美國核第一時間(first strikes) 能力<br />\n望清楚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"